text: Oranmore may refer to: * Oranmore, a town on the outskirts of the city of Galway in Ireland ** Oranmore Castle, a castle in the town of Oranmore, County Galway * Oranmore, Ontario, a community in the township of Magnetawan, Ontario, Canada ==See also== *Oran Mor (disambiguation)
title: Oranmore (disambiguation)
